  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is our goal to study the mechanism of ischemia-reperfusion injury. Our DIEP-operation is
      actually a clinical model of ischemia-reperfusion. Ischemia-reperfusion injury has never been
      directly studied in a human, clinical model of autologous transplant.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
